OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1771883656
OL,3,CReform UK: Proposed deportation force
OL,4,Cwill not be 'UK version of ICE'
OL,6,FReform UK's proposed agency to carry
OL,7,Fout mass deportations of migrants with
OL,8,Fno right to be in the country will not
OL,9,Fbecome like Donald Trump's Ice
OL,10,Fprogramme in the US, its home affairs
OL,11,Fspokesman has said.
OL,13,FZia Yusuf said it is "not true" that
OL,14,Fthe party's plans for a UK Deportation
OL,15,FCommand will face the same issues as
OL,16,FUS president Mr Trump's body, which
OL,17,Fsaw an immigration crackdown in
OL,18,FMinnesota lead to mass detentions,
OL,19,Fprotests and two deaths.
OL,26,@uD@VOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
