PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1771883656
OL,3,CReform UK: Proposed deportation force
OL,4,Cwill not be 'UK version of ICE'
OL,6,FUnder a Reform government, the party
OL,7,Fwould set up the unit to "track down,
OL,8,Fdetain and deport" people in the
OL,9,Fcountry illegally, aiming for up to
OL,10,F288,000 people each year.
OL,12,FMr Yusuf said it was "very tempting"
OL,13,Fand "somewhat inevitable" for people
OL,14,Fto make the comparison between
OL,15,FReform's model and the US, but said
OL,16,Fthe UK does not have the same problems
OL,17,Fwith firearms and policing is "much
OL,18,Fmore" done by consent.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@RO]tD@VOUtD@dO]uD@EOUuD@YO]yD@
OL,26,A_OUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
