OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1771883656
OL,3,CReform UK: Proposed deportation force
OL,4,Cwill not be 'UK version of ICE'
OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference in
OL,7,FDover, he said: "So you know this
OL,8,Fnotion that we're going to have the
OL,9,Fsame issues that come sharply into
OL,10,Ffocus internationally as a result of
OL,11,FTrump's Ice programme ` it's just not
OL,12,Ftrue, we would not expect UK
OL,13,FDeportation Command to carry weapons.
OL,14,FIt's not going to be the case.
OL,16,F"But I also want to be clear that if
OL,17,Fyou're in this country illegally, they
OL,18,Fwill detect you and they will detain
OL,19,Fyou and they'll deport you."
OL,26,@oD@QOUxD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1771883656
OL,3,CReform UK: Proposed deportation force
OL,4,Cwill not be 'UK version of ICE'
OL,6,FHe added: "If your question is: are we
OL,7,Fgoing to have the kind of situation
OL,8,Fthat we saw in Minnesota in Britain as
OL,9,Fa result of our deportation programme?
OL,10,FNo."
OL,12,FLiberal Democrat home affairs
OL,13,Fspokesman Max Wilkinson had said
OL,14,FReform's "Trump-inspired plans for an
OL,15,FIce-style force will only bring chaos
OL,16,Fand disorder to Britain's streets, not
OL,17,Fthe order and control our immigration
OL,18,Fsystem needs".
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@DO]vD@JOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
