OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1771883656
OL,3,CReform UK: Proposed deportation force
OL,4,Cwill not be 'UK version of ICE'
OL,6,FAmnesty International UK also warned
OL,7,Fthe UK does not "need or want" a
OL,8,FBritish version of ICE and such
OL,9,Fproposals to mirror the US "risk
OL,10,Funleashing a system built on fear,
OL,11,Faggressive raids and discrimination,
OL,12,Fwhere enforcement operates with
OL,13,Fsweeping powers and little
OL,14,Faccountability."
OL,16,FIn Dover on Monday, Mr Yusuf said the
OL,17,FUK is being "invaded" by migrants as
OL,18,Fhe pitched Reform's mass deportation
OL,19,Fprogramme as the biggest in UK history.
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@^O]qD@\OUvD@PO]yD@MOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1771883656
OL,3,CReform UK: Proposed deportation force
OL,4,Cwill not be 'UK version of ICE'
OL,6,FThe party has also said it will impose
OL,7,F"visa freezes" on Pakistan,
OL,8,FAfghanistan and Syria if the countries
OL,9,Frefuse to take back migrants with n
OL,11,Fo legal right to stay in Britain.
OL,13,FReform has said it would expect to
OL,14,Fdeport more than 600,000 in its first
OL,15,Fterm in government.
OL,17,FDefending his choice of language, Mr
OL,18,FYusuf told a press conference in
OL,19,FDover: "I know many in the
OL,20,Festablishment gasp at that word.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@NO]{D@HOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1771883656
OL,3,CReform UK: Proposed deportation force
OL,4,Cwill not be 'UK version of ICE'
OL,6,F"They may well clutch their pearls in
OL,7,Fthe television studios, but the
OL,8,Fdictionary definition of invasion is
OL,9,Fan incursion by a large number of
OL,10,Fpeople in an unwanted way.
OL,12,F"Make no mistake, as home secretary I
OL,13,Fwill end and indeed reverse this
OL,14,Finvasion, because the patience of the
OL,15,FBritish people is now exhausted."
OL,17,FMr Yusuf also said the rights of
OL,18,FBritish citizens are being placed
OL,19,F"beneath those of criminals" because
OL,20,Fof the European Convention on Human
OL,21,FRights (ECHR).
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@aO]{D@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1771883656
OL,3,CReform UK: Proposed deportation force
OL,4,Cwill not be 'UK version of ICE'
OL,6,FThe party has pledged to leave the
OL,7,Ftreaty.
OL,9,FMr Yusuf listed what he said were
OL,10,Fexamples of judges blocking the
OL,11,Fdeportation of illegal migrants who
OL,12,Fhad committed crimes.
OL,14,F"How many more people must die at the
OL,15,Fhands of those who should never have
OL,16,Fbeen in our country in the first
OL,17,Fplace?" he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1771883656
OL,3,CReform UK: Proposed deportation force
OL,4,Cwill not be 'UK version of ICE'
OL,6,F"How many more victims' families must
OL,7,Fbe devastated in this way when their
OL,8,Frights are placed beneath those of
OL,9,Fcriminals?
OL,11,F"The answer is none. Vote Reform. We
OL,12,Fwill leave the ECHR and end this
OL,13,Fmadness."
OL,15,FReacting to the speech, shadow home
OL,16,Fsecretary Chris Phlip said Mr Yusuf
OL,17,Fhas "nothing new to offer beyond
OL,18,Fcopying and pasting Conservative
OL,19,Fplans".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@IO]yD@EOU{D@FO]
